.\n\n### HTML Worker — ok\nThe HTML file has been created successfully with **zero validation errors**. Here's a summary of what was built:\n\n## ✅ Complete: `index.html`\n\n### Structure Overview\n\n| Section | Semantic Element | Content Source |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Header / Nav** | `<header>` → `<nav>` | Logo + 5 links: Home, Features, Dashboard, Community, Get Started |\n| **Hero** | `<section>` with `aria-labelledby` | H1: *\"Transform Every Step into Progress\"* + CTA buttons + hero banner image |\n| **Features** | `<section>` → 3 `<article>` cards with `role=\"listitem\"` | Activity Logging, Progress Visualization, Smart Goal Setting — each with an icon, H3, and full descriptive paragraph |\n| **CTA Section** | `<section>` | *\"Ready to Redefine What You're Capable Of?\"* with \"Create Your Free Account\" and \"Explore Features\" |\n| **Footer** | `<footer>` with `role=\"contentinfo\"` | Navigation links, social links (Instagram, YouTube, TikTok, X), email, copyright |\n\n### Images Generated (4 total)\n- `images/hero-banner.jpg` — Runner at golden sunrise with PulsePro UI overlay\n- `images/icon-activity-logging.png` — Teal running figure with sync waves\n- `images/icon-progress-visualization.png` — Purple ascending line graph\n- `images/icon-goal-setting.png` — Orange bullseye target with checkmark\n\n### Accessibility Features\n- `aria-labelledby` on each section referencing its heading `id`\n- `aria-label` on navigation and social link blocks\n- `aria-hidden=\"true\"` on decorative icons (feature icons are presentational)\n- Desc\n\n### CSS Worker — error\nERROR: No streaming chunk received for 120.0s (model=deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash, chunks_received=544). The connection may be alive at the TCP layer but is not producing content. Tune or disable via the `stream_chunk_timeout` constructor kwarg (set to None or 0 to disable) or the `LANGCHAIN_OPENAI_STREAM_CHUNK_TIMEOUT_S` env var. See also `http_socket_options` for the kernel-level TCP timeout that catches